#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a von Mises distribution."
msgstr "从冯·米塞斯分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from a von Mises distribution with specified mode (mu) "
"and dispersion (kappa), on the interval [-pi, pi]."
msgstr "从具有指定模式（mu）和离散度（kappa）的冯·米塞斯分布中抽取样本，区间为 [-pi, pi]。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:6 of
msgid ""
"The von Mises distribution (also known as the circular normal "
"distribution) is a continuous probability distribution on the unit "
"circle.  It may be thought of as the circular analogue of the normal "
"distribution."
msgstr "冯·米塞斯分布（也称为圆形正态分布）是单位圆上的连续概率分布。它可被视为正态分布的圆形类比。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:11 of
msgid "Mode (\"center\") of the distribution."
msgstr "分布的模式（“中心”）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:13 of
msgid "Dispersion of the distribution, has to be >=0."
msgstr "分布的离散度，必须 >=0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:15 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``mu`` and ``kappa`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``np.broadcast(mu, kappa).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则会抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），并且 ``mu`` 和 ``kappa`` 都是标量，"
"则返回单个值。否则，抽取 ``np.broadcast(mu, kappa).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:20 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:22 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:24 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:27 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized von Mises distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的冯·米塞斯分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.vonmises`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:33 of
msgid ""
"probability density function, distribution, or cumulative density "
"function, etc."
msgstr "概率密度函数、分布或累积密度函数等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:36 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:37 of
msgid "The probability density for the von Mises distribution is"
msgstr "冯·米塞斯分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:39 of
msgid ""
"p(x) = \\frac{e^{\\kappa cos(x-\\mu)}}{2\\pi I_0(\\kappa)},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:41 of
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\mu` is the mode and :math:`\\kappa` the dispersion, and "
":math:`I_0(\\kappa)` is the modified Bessel function of order 0."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`\\mu` 是模式，:math:`\\kappa` 是离散度，:math:`I_0(\\kappa)` "
"是 0 阶修正贝塞尔函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:44 of
msgid ""
"The von Mises is named for Richard Edler von Mises, who was born in "
"Austria-Hungary, in what is now the Ukraine.  He fled to the United "
"States in 1939 and became a professor at Harvard.  He worked in "
"probability theory, aerodynamics, fluid mechanics, and philosophy of "
"science."
msgstr ""
"冯·米塞斯以理查德·埃德勒·冯·米塞斯命名，他出生在奥匈帝国，即现在的乌克兰"
"。他于1939年逃到美国，并成为哈佛大学的教授。他从事概率论、空气动力学、"
"流体力学和科学哲学的研究。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:51 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:52 of
msgid ""
"Abramowitz, M. and Stegun, I. A. (Eds.). \"Handbook of Mathematical "
"Functions with Formulas, Graphs, and Mathematical Tables, 9th printing,\""
" New York: Dover, 1972."
msgstr ""
"Abramowitz, M. 和 Stegun, I. A. (编). \"数学函数手册：公式、图表和数学表"
"，第9版，\" 纽约：Dover，1972年。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.vonmises.vonmises:55 of
msgid ""
"von Mises, R., \"Mathematical Theory of Probability and Statistics\", New"
" York: Academic Press, 1964."
msgstr "von Mises, R., \"概率与统计的数学理论\", 纽约: Academic Press, 1964."

